On #GivingTuesday, President Donald Trump and First Lady Melania Trump issued a statement encouraging Americans to help those in need through acts of compassion and generosity. They emphasized the philanthropic spirit of the American people and highlighted the remarkable stories of citizens assisting their neighbors. The President urged individuals to seek opportunities to improve the lives of others and their communities, whether through volunteering at shelters, donating to organizations supporting the military, or promoting childhood literacy. The First Lady joined the President in expressing gratitude to those who have contributed to the well-being of the country and fellow Americans, and they both reaffirmed their commitment to strengthening the bonds that unite the nation by helping others.